PrecisAcceptance of an amendment of a designation wherein the KAMLOOPS BAND surrendered, for an unspecified term, some 1,000 acres of land on Kamloops Indian Reserve No. 1 in British Columbia for leasing purposes (P.C. 1996-515 of April 26, 1996); the amendment will change the named lessee for one of the five projects in the designation.
